{"tid":41783,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解當初四眼要已讀不回梁天琦既信息？","createTime":"2016-12-16T07:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T03:37:12.000Z","uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33fe92c19119128ade1f2e59cd0d3cd5b0a43a2a","tid":41783,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"跟據返當日梁天琦打上神駒到解釋<br />\n1:43:10開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=xIH5KzMdevo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshared%3Fci%3DxIH5KzMdevo&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=50f0a32a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=xIH5KzMdevo</a><br />\n佢係喺25/8下午4點幾send過message比四眼話想endorse佢<br />\n但一路直到27/8下午1點55分先回應返佢<br />\n而毓民屌天琦個陣正正係27/8既朝早<br />\n即係話四眼喺天琦比教主屌完後先覆返天琦<br />\n咁點解佢又無同毓民解釋返有呢單野？<br />\n定其實佢地兩個一早都知有呢單野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60abd2e86f85d39b0e3a1fe382b7be0d0d37926","tid":41783,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc5d1f9d031b5027d534980e4b87d151e13e6815","tid":41783,"uid":19211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"係囡先秒回是常識吧，難道連登一個玩家都無？"},{"pid":"642fc97f092f2adc54d39106e110c8953625816f","tid":41783,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"如果當初四眼同毓民講返有件事<br />\n咁毓民會唔會收返佢既言論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3844a623713583828faa947c956cadbf49671b","tid":41783,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"根本成個局黎，見本民前同青政威脅到佢地利益，咪靠呢D野希望中傷人地拉返D票。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820d925d0ef04a3551865f23b4bca55f6f89481d","tid":41783,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本成個